{"tid":2301413,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"拾下拾下算唔算黃子華表現最出色嘅一期棟篤笑？","createTime":"2020-11-26T09:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T06:22:48.000Z","uid":365620,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"82ee1248efcc41bcdc7897cb2ef838b1f6b1ba89","tid":2301413,"uid":365620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nSe3nhopbpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnSe3nhopbpg&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=41e26fcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nSe3nhopbpg</a><br />\n<br />\n成場嘅topic轉換都十分自然流暢<br />\n唔似後來幾期需要用音樂嚟做切割<br />\n講講下又可以連返去之前嘅topic <br />\n而且有幾個topic其實幾發人深省<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如建設社會同拍戲生涯嗰part(當然唔止咁少）<br />\n<br />\n金句唔駛講<br />\n人生三大矛盾去到今時今日都仲聽到<br />\n<br />\n仲要無論睇幾多次<br />\n睇到識背咁濟<br />\n都總有啲位會令到你發笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2632bbf96f12268d1c3eddd03a221f5dc61f3166","tid":2301413,"uid":263183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T10:50:47.000Z","msg":"好多人揀拾下拾下<br />\n不過個人最中意第一套娛樂圈血肉史，跟住末世財神/色情家庭/秋前，之後無炭/拾下拾下"},{"pid":"21bc3c971b847fe2b6cdd4aa05a0fc7b9627002c","tid":2301413,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2632bbf96f12268d1c3eddd03a221f5dc61f3166","tid":2301413,"uid":263183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T10:50:47.000Z","msg":"好多人揀拾下拾下<br />\n不過個人最中意第一套娛樂圈血肉史，跟住末世財神/色情家庭/秋前，之後無炭/拾下拾下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"娛樂圈血肉史/末世財神/色情家庭/秋前 我都覺得好有味道。無炭/拾下拾下比較主流"},{"pid":"b98f0a44e6aa3032e522b06aa48990093d004c3f","tid":2301413,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21bc3c971b847fe2b6cdd4aa05a0fc7b9627002c","tid":2301413,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2632bbf96f12268d1c3eddd03a221f5dc61f3166","tid":2301413,"uid":263183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"